                <p>Holy, holy, holy (Lord of Sabaoth)</p>
            </div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Good condition. The inscription appears in abbreviated form rather than the earlier one used in Panagia tou Arakos' church at Lagoudera as complete word. The text is from the Isaiah 6:13 and it is referred in the Divine Liturgy in the Victory's hymn (Epinikios Ymnos) </p>
